DelegatedWork.adminDisplayName: Perform user-impacting remote actions on Microsoft Intune devices
DelegatedWork.adminDescription: Allows the app to perform remote high impact actions such as wiping the device or resetting the passcode on devices managed by Microsoft Intune.
DelegatedWork.userDisplayName: Perform user-impacting remote actions on Microsoft Intune devices
DelegatedWork.userDescription: Allows the app to perform remote high impact actions such as wiping the device or resetting the passcode on devices managed by Microsoft Intune.

Application.adminDisplayName: Perform user-impacting remote actions on Microsoft Intune devices
Application.adminDescription: Allows the app to perform remote high impact actions such as wiping the device or resetting the passcode on devices managed by Microsoft Intune, without a signed-in user.

DelegatedWork.adminDescription: Allows the app to read the properties of devices managed by Microsoft Intune.
DelegatedWork.userDescription: Allows the app to read the properties of devices managed by Microsoft Intune.

Application.adminDescription: Allows the app to read the properties of devices managed by Microsoft Intune, without a signed-in user.

DelegatedWork.adminDisplayName: Read and write Microsoft Intune devices
DelegatedWork.adminDescription: Allows the app to read and write the properties of devices managed by Microsoft Intune. Does not allow high impact operations such as remote wipe and password reset on the device’s owner.
DelegatedWork.userDisplayName: Read and write Microsoft Intune devices
DelegatedWork.userDescription: Allows the app to read and write the properties of devices managed by Microsoft Intune. Does not allow high impact operations such as remote wipe and password reset on the device’s owner.

Application.adminDisplayName: Read and write Microsoft Intune devices
Application.adminDescription: Allows the app to read and write the properties of devices managed by Microsoft Intune, without a signed-in user. Does not allow high impact operations such as remote wipe and password reset on the device’s owner
